description: The Bay Area's best frozen treats are rolling right to you, thanks to Fairyella Ice Pops! Organic, vegan goodness on the go is always a welcome treat when you're out and about on a sunny California day. As an added bonus, Fairyella the Toothfairy can personally show up to hand out the Ice Pops! Great taste and lots of nutrients are all packed into a delicious package that your sweet tooth is sure to love, thanks to Fairyella!
name: Fairyella Ice Pops
